            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp [<span class=\"text-purple\">7 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [10 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
